{
    "publish_date": "2015-03-19T11:53:09.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT6M55S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "Ride is my life", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "7.954"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The man and his motorcycle", 
            "dur": "1.62", 
            "start": "10.62"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The power of nature", 
            "dur": "2.3", 
            "start": "12.9"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The noise of the trees, the gust of the wind", 
            "dur": "3.26", 
            "start": "15.9"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The sound of the rocks", 
            "dur": "1.555", 
            "start": "19.16"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "To be one flesh with your beauty", 
            "dur": "2.46", 
            "start": "21.38"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You\u2019re talking too much and bikes are made to ride", 
            "dur": "1.7", 
            "start": "25.62"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Julien Perret has no squared shirt", 
            "dur": "2.06", 
            "start": "33.96"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and we don\u2019t care", 
            "dur": "1.054", 
            "start": "36.02"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because on a bike this trialist if far from being clumsy", 
            "dur": "3.72", 
            "start": "37.08"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The ideal kind of person to see what this new Ducati", 
            "dur": "3.68", 
            "start": "41.16"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "has in the guts concerning off-road", 
            "dur": "1.46", 
            "start": "44.84"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Isn\u2019t the scrambler supposed to be the trail ancestor ?", 
            "dur": "2.72", 
            "start": "46.3"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And there\u2019s grappler tires on it yes or non ?", 
            "dur": "2.42", 
            "start": "49.02"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In this rather violent kind of exercises", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "51.735"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the Italian bike has some assets", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "53.88"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "such as a quite low saddle", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "56.128"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a high handlebar that eases standing position", 
            "dur": "2.892", 
            "start": "58.128"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and a rather light weight of 189 kilograms", 
            "dur": "2.5", 
            "start": "61.54"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "allowing to ride fast without being carried away", 
            "dur": "3.84", 
            "start": "64.04"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Is it slate or schist ?", 
            "dur": "1.54", 
            "start": "68.72"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Engine wise, that\u2019s a very good thing that Ducati", 
            "dur": "3.24", 
            "start": "73.84"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "opted for a small air-cooled twin of 803cc", 
            "dur": "3.16", 
            "start": "77.08"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that\u2019s strong-built seeing how much", 
            "dur": "2.2", 
            "start": "80.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Julien is mistreating the Scrambler", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "82.7"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we\u2019re glad that there\u2019s no fragile elements", 
            "dur": "2.12", 
            "start": "84.7"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "such as a radiator or coolant reservoir", 
            "dur": "2.64", 
            "start": "86.82"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "careful though, the oil filter under the engine", 
            "dur": "3.18", 
            "start": "89.94"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "ended up this review really bumped", 
            "dur": "2.5", 
            "start": "93.46"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And with 75hp, we can\u2019t say that the power is wicked", 
            "dur": "4.48", 
            "start": "96.44"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So the bike is punchy with a gauging throttle", 
            "dur": "3.8", 
            "start": "101.24"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Also the back tire is not out-powered ", 
            "dur": "1.86", 
            "start": "105.28"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and keeps a good drive", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "107.14"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So how does this Ducati behaves off-road ?", 
            "dur": "2.5", 
            "start": "109.954"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well great, it really matches its road skills", 
            "dur": "5.96", 
            "start": "112.84"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Sure it\u2019s a road bike but to get in battered fields", 
            "dur": "5.76", 
            "start": "119.04"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it\u2019s light and handy enough with the right suspensions", 
            "dur": "4.36", 
            "start": "125.2"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Is it a real scrambler ? I mean able to get in trails...", 
            "dur": "4.64", 
            "start": "129.56"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "yeah definitely able to drive in trails", 
            "dur": "2.34", 
            "start": "134.2"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "as long as the ground isn&#39;t too rough I think it\u2019sgood", 
            "dur": "5.98", 
            "start": "136.54"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the only weakness would be the ground clearance", 
            "dur": "2.76", 
            "start": "143.06"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we tend to scrap a bit and that\u2019s a shame", 
            "dur": "4.26", 
            "start": "145.82"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Ok remove the fake beard you\u2019re ridiculous", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "150.615"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And go ride now", 
            "dur": "0.82", 
            "start": "152.615"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In the end we listened Julien and went for a ride", 
            "dur": "2.82", 
            "start": "167.74"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but without the beard as it\u2019s itchy with the helmet", 
            "dur": "2.98", 
            "start": "170.56"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The Scrambler is the most accessible Ducati", 
            "dur": "3.52", 
            "start": "173.86"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We get on it as if it was a large moped", 
            "dur": "2.98", 
            "start": "177.38"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and within 10km you\u2019ve already find your feet", 
            "dur": "2.44", 
            "start": "180.72"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The clutch lever is soft and the maneuverability evident", 
            "dur": "3.8", 
            "start": "183.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It could be a driver\u2019s-ed bike", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "187.48"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the rather soft and comfy suspensions", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "189.608"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "are nevertheless decent at road-handling", 
            "dur": "3.96", 
            "start": "191.76"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "By the way the Pirelli MT-60", 
            "dur": "2.6", 
            "start": "195.98"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "aren\u2019t giving much feedback to the rider", 
            "dur": "2.86", 
            "start": "198.58"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but as for the grip it\u2019s holding out", 
            "dur": "2.22", 
            "start": "201.78"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the more the curves are coming", 
            "dur": "2.26", 
            "start": "204.3"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the more we have fun swinging the Ducati", 
            "dur": "2.16", 
            "start": "206.56"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with more and more confidence", 
            "dur": "1.675", 
            "start": "208.72"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and we ride with peace of mind", 
            "dur": "2.52", 
            "start": "211"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "admiring this wonderful Cevennes landscape", 
            "dur": "3.56", 
            "start": "213.92"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What\u2019s good with the Scrambler is that", 
            "dur": "1.54", 
            "start": "236.954"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it\u2019s that&#39;s not only for the posh but for beasts too", 
            "dur": "2.44", 
            "start": "238.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In sport situations we see the bike\u2019s limits", 
            "dur": "3.68", 
            "start": "241.46"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The Italian brand presents it as a beginner\u2019s bike", 
            "dur": "3.52", 
            "start": "245.44"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So it&#39;s obvious that it\u2019s less efficient than a 821 Monster", 
            "dur": "3.34", 
            "start": "249.14"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But pure performances aside", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "252.48"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that allow already a good pace", 
            "dur": "2.44", 
            "start": "254.48"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we\u2019re not fully satisfied with the machine\u2019s temper", 
            "dur": "3.22", 
            "start": "257.36"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The Scrambler barely vibrates", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "260.848"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "has a rather discreet sound", 
            "dur": "1.947", 
            "start": "262.848"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the engine has quite linear accelerations", 
            "dur": "3.06", 
            "start": "265.06"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with a flat torque curve", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "268.4"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that peaks at 7mkg around 5 900 rpm", 
            "dur": "3.36", 
            "start": "270.4"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we would have liked more personality", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "274.34"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a stronger nature with the little thing", 
            "dur": "3.14", 
            "start": "276.76"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that is crispy", 
            "dur": "1.02", 
            "start": "279.9"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In other word we would have wanted this new Ducati", 
            "dur": "3.32", 
            "start": "281.34"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "more like a true Ducati", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "284.9"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But only in motion as in static the Italians stroke hard", 
            "dur": "4.44", 
            "start": "287.22"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well the Italians\u2026 or should I say THE French", 
            "dur": "3.04", 
            "start": "292.06"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "As the Scrambler is the art of the young Julien Cl\u00e9ment", 
            "dur": "3.92", 
            "start": "295.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Pure and with no fancies", 
            "dur": "1.86", 
            "start": "299.34"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The bike&#39;s design is clearly a surgical strike", 
            "dur": "2.06", 
            "start": "301.48"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And even though it\u2019s a small bike", 
            "dur": "1.84", 
            "start": "303.88"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the Ducati is a genuine eye-magnet", 
            "dur": "2.74", 
            "start": "305.96"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We appreciate details such as the engine\u2019s cooling fins ", 
            "dur": "4.1", 
            "start": "308.7"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the original metal-plates on the tank", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "313.08"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the nicely designed and comfy saddle", 
            "dur": "2.56", 
            "start": "316.54"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "even if the passenger seat is restrained", 
            "dur": "3.28", 
            "start": "319.34"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the shock is easily accessible and adjustable in preload", 
            "dur": "3.42", 
            "start": "323.14"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The front disk has a disconnectable ABS", 
            "dur": "3.28", 
            "start": "327"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and a large brembo radial caliper", 
            "dur": "2.32", 
            "start": "330.54"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "At last the dash offers a trip report, a clock", 
            "dur": "4.04", 
            "start": "333.2"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and a tachometer all around the digital display", 
            "dur": "2.98", 
            "start": "337.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It has to be noted that everything\u2019s controlled at handle", 
            "dur": "2.74", 
            "start": "340.48"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And for the fashionable guys, as well as the icon", 
            "dur": "3.74", 
            "start": "343.22"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "there\u2019s other versions:", 
            "dur": "1.375", 
            "start": "346.96"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the urban enduro, the classic and the full-throttle", 
            "dur": "3.34", 
            "start": "348.34"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "As well as a complete accessories and clothing line", 
            "dur": "3.9", 
            "start": "352.16"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We can\u2019t say otherwise: ", 
            "dur": "0.92", 
            "start": "356.44"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the Scramble is a fashionable bike with a great design", 
            "dur": "4.62", 
            "start": "357.36"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The ideal machine to show-off on the roads", 
            "dur": "3.5", 
            "start": "361.98"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and attract girls, especially those already lured", 
            "dur": "4.08", 
            "start": "365.48"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "by the vintage and the bearded posh fashion", 
            "dur": "2.88", 
            "start": "369.56"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Hey babe ! Wanna go for a ride ?", 
            "dur": "2.92", 
            "start": "372.44"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "With pleasure !", 
            "dur": "1.18", 
            "start": "375.84"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Hey my bike !", 
            "dur": "1.14", 
            "start": "379.24"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "On the Ducati Scrambler", 
            "dur": "1.66", 
            "start": "383.42"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we liked", 
            "dur": "0.8", 
            "start": "385.62"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The bike&#39;s agility", 
            "dur": "1.6", 
            "start": "386.7"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The accessible saddle height", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "388.76"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The pure and cool design", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "391.074"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The easy handling", 
            "dur": "1.82", 
            "start": "393.38"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The rather soft engine", 
            "dur": "1.815", 
            "start": "395.2"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We disliked", 
            "dur": "0.94", 
            "start": "397.52"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "A slight lack of temper", 
            "dur": "2.6", 
            "start": "398.46"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The false neutral position of the gearbox", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "401.255"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And squared shirts", 
            "dur": "1.22", 
            "start": "403.255"
        }
